OL,3,CWho else is named in abuse review
OL,4,Cwhich triggered Welby's resignation?
OL,6,FA number of other names have been
OL,7,Fnoted in the Makin Review for their
OL,8,Ffailings regarding the Smyth abuse
OL,9,Fscandal - but who are they?
OL,11,FStephen Conway and Yvonne Quirk
OL,13,FStephen Conway, the current Bishop of
OL,14,FLincoln, was Bishop of Ely in 2013
OL,15,Fwhen he was briefed on Smyth's abuse
OL,16,Fby Yvonne Quirk, his safeguarding
OL,17,Fadvisor.
