OL,6,FMr Conway had agreed to find support
OL,7,Ffor a victim and to contact the
OL,8,FArchbishop of Canterbury and the
OL,9,FBishop of Cape Town.
OL,11,FHe then wrote to the Bishop of Table
OL,12,FBay, detailing the severity of the
OL,13,Fabuse, Smyth's links to the Iwerne
OL,14,FChristian summer camps, an assumed
OL,15,Freferral to Cambridgeshire Police and
OL,16,Fa reference to how speedily Smyth left
OL,17,Fthe UK.
