OL,3,CWho else is named in abuse review
OL,4,Cwhich triggered Welby's resignation?
OL,6,FYvonne Quirk told the review that,
OL,7,Fafter meeting with officers from
OL,8,FCambridgeshire Police, she was told
OL,9,Fthe case couldn't be taken further as
OL,10,Fa police matter - and believed there
OL,11,Fwas "no possibility of a criminal
OL,12,Finvestigation".
OL,14,FJo Bailey Wells
OL,16,FThe Rev Jo Bailey Wells, currently the
OL,17,FBishop for Episcopal Ministry in the
OL,18,FAnglican Communion, was the personal
OL,19,Fchaplain to the Archbishop of
OL,20,FCanterbury in 2013.
