OL,3,CWho else is named in abuse review
OL,4,Cwhich triggered Welby's resignation?
OL,6,FStephen Conway emailed her, attaching
OL,7,Fthe letter he had sent to the Bishop
OL,8,Fof Table Bay detailing Smyth's abuse.
OL,10,FShe replied, saying she would let the
OL,11,FArchbishop of Canterbury know and
OL,12,Fnoted that Mr Welby might know Smyth.
OL,14,FAfter forwarding on the information,
OL,15,Fshe advised in September that no
OL,16,Ffurther action should be taken until
OL,17,Fpolice had advised on the next steps.
