OL,3,CWho else is named in abuse review
OL,4,Cwhich triggered Welby's resignation?
OL,6,FThe review stated that the police
OL,7,Fadvice "never came to fruition" and
OL,8,Fthat there was "no evidence in the
OL,9,FLambeth Palace records passed to
OL,10,FReviewers to indicate that Jo Bailey
OL,11,FWells followed this up".
OL,13,FBefore being ordained to become a
OL,14,Fchurch officer, Sue Colman agreed to
OL,15,Fbecome a trustee of Zambesi Trust
OL,16,FBoard, despite knowing about Smyth's
OL,17,Fabuse.
OL,19,FAccording to the review, Mrs Colman
OL,20,Fwas reluctant to be a trustee due to
OL,21,Fher knowledge of the abuse.
