OL,6,FThe review, referring to Mrs Colman
OL,7,Fand her husband Sir Jamie Colman, a
OL,8,Ffellow trustee, added: "It is likely,
OL,9,Fon the balance of probabilities, that
OL,10,Fboth Jamie and Sue Colman had
OL,11,Fsignificant knowledge of the abuses in
OL,12,Fthe UK and Africa, given their
OL,13,Fpositions as Trustees."
OL,15,FThe Colmans also funded the Smyths
OL,16,Fthrough a personal trust.
